\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid14303659\charrsid12206042  (?? \endash  sp. 19.18) \endash  patron/client relations \endash  a lot of noblesse oblige and all that sort of stuff, increasingly, as the 
